             was indicted for <rs id="t17980418-17-off74" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980418-17-off74" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980418-17-off74" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
